problem to be addressed by the pope 
mandela leader of the african national congress is on a 
sixweek tour of europe africa and north america in part to 
persuade foreign governments to maintain the sanctions despite 
recent reforms by south african president fw de klerk 
john paul received mandela in a 25minute audience 
