respect from the whole world 
john paul replied in english god bless your initiatives 
in a statement the vatican said the audience granted to mandela 
was further confirmation of the holy sees commitment in favor of 
a peaceful political evolution in south africa and the 
progressive overcoming of the system of apartheid 
it said such changes should lead to a society based on 
pacification and reconciliation among all components of that 
nation with the guaranteeing and respect of the fundamental rights 
of all citizens 
