proceeds from the sales will be earmarked to provide food 
assistance to needy families and to help farmers in projects to 
increase production and marketing 
dickerson said the program is carried out by the us agency for 
international development 
the corn donation boosts honduran food aid to 34 million from 
an initial 12 million announced on march 9 he said 
