<TEXT>
here are some facts about 
nelson mandela 
name nelson rolihlahla mandela 
age 71 
born july 18 1918 in transkei the son of a xhosa tribal 
chief 
title deputy president of the african national congress 
arrested august 5 1962 
sentenced november 1962 to five years hard labor for leaving 
the country illegally and inciting blacks to violate the law by 
striking sentenced in june 1964 to life imprisonment for sabotage 
and plotting to overthrow the government 
imprisoned 27 years 
released february 11 1990 
current political objective mandela says dialogue between the 
south african government and the anc is the only way to a peaceful 
future he wants the government to free all prisoners convicted of 
politically motivated crimes stop police from firing on black 
protesters and end the state of emergency in the natal province 
where anc supporters are battling members of the rival inkatha 
organization 
when those conditions are met he says the anc and the 
government can enter into negotiations apparently including other 
