perceived as the party that fights for a reduction in the capital 
gains tax while we turn our backs on taxpaying hardworking 
american families who are in medical crisis she said 
bush according to his spokesmen supports voluntary leave but 
contends that forcing employers to provide the leave amounts to 
excessive government intervention in the workplace 
democrats confident that the measure is popular with voters 
