disappointed by the lack of one 
ive learned long ago you dont argue about a victory when you 
get one he said im also convinced that had it come to a 
recorded vote we would have prevailed 
dodd acknowledged he might not have enough votes in the senate 
to override a veto but said he was close 
opponents contend the bill would be costly and burdensome for 
businesses and represents a government intrusion into affairs best 
left to business and labor supporters said nearly all 
industrialized nations already provide such minimum job security to 
workers and many have provisions for full or partial pay 
the bill also would cover federal employees with even more 
generous leave provisions it would cover house employees but not 
employees of the senate 
