here is a chronology of recent developments in 
donald trumps life 
september 1980 trump opens the grand hyatt hotel restored 
with the help of a 120 million new york city tax break 
april 1983 trump tower complete with marble atrium and 
waterfall opens on fifth avenue in new york and becomes the citys 
newest tourist attraction giving trump nationwide fame 
fall 1983 trump buys new jersey generals of the united states 
football league 
1987 writes trump the art of the deal 
may 14 1984 harrahs hotelcasino at trump plaza opens in 
atlantic city nj the harrahs reference later was dropped from 
the name 
june 17 1985 trump castle hotelcasino opens in atlantic city 
august 1986 usfl including new jersey generals suspends 
season 
march 31 1989 trump buys eastern airlines shuttle between 
boston new york and washington the 365 million deal is a 
revision of an agreement reached in october 1988 
oct 10 three top trump casino executives are killed in a 
helicopter crash as they return to atlantic city from new york 
february 1990 reports surface that trump and his wife ivana of 
13 years are considering divorce model marla maples is linked 
romantically to trump 
april 2 trumps taj mahal hotelcasino opens in atlantic city 
april 27 the wall street journal publishes a story in which 
trump discloses he is considering selling the shuttle to raise 
cash trump insists he is not having cashflow trouble but simply 
wants to be in a better position to take advantage of the slumping 
real estate market 
june 11 trump confirms a tentative agreement with bankers that 
would provide him another 60 million in loans and a temporary 
suspension of debt payments in exchange the banks would get 
equity in some of his properties 
june 15 trump misses a payment deadline for interest and 
principal on bonds for trump castle after failing to get a final 
agreement with the banks negotiations continue with bankers over a 
bailout 
